			<div class="content" id="post-content-1559252">
									

<p>BTW, for the time being, all original creepypasta pages <em>must</em> also be tagged with 'tale'. And non-original creepypasta must also be tagged with 'delete', because we're going to remove them from the site soon. (I covered the latter already, and most of the former as well, excepting articles from the past couple weeks.)</p>
